### API Endpoint Test Suite
### GET /api/regions
@endpointUrl = {{baseUrl}}/api/regions

### NOTE: This endpoint does NOT require authentication (public read access)
### Regions are global reference data accessible to all users

### ============================================================================
### SUCCESS CASES
### ============================================================================

### Test 1: List regions with default pagination (happy path)
### Expected: 200 OK with up to 20 regions
GET {{endpointUrl}}

### Test 2: List regions with custom page and limit
### Expected: 200 OK with requested page size
GET {{endpointUrl}}?page=1&limit=10

### Test 3: List regions with search (case-insensitive)
### Expected: 200 OK with regions matching search term
GET {{endpointUrl}}?search=uji

### Test 4: List regions with search and pagination
### Expected: 200 OK with filtered and paginated results
GET {{endpointUrl}}?search=japan&page=1&limit=5

### Test 5: List regions with limit=100 (maximum allowed)
### Expected: 200 OK with up to 100 regions
GET {{endpointUrl}}?limit=100

### Test 6: List regions with search (no matches)
### Expected: 200 OK with empty data array
GET {{endpointUrl}}?search=nonexistentregionxyz12345

### Test 7: List regions with empty search string
### Expected: 200 OK with all regions (search ignored)
GET {{endpointUrl}}?search=

### Test 8: List regions - page beyond available pages
### Expected: 200 OK with empty data array
GET {{endpointUrl}}?page=999&limit=50

### ============================================================================
### VALIDATION ERROR CASES (400 Bad Request)
### ============================================================================

### Test 9: Invalid page (zero)
### Expected: 400 Bad Request - page must be positive
GET {{endpointUrl}}?page=0

### Test 10: Invalid page (negative)
### Expected: 400 Bad Request - page must be positive
GET {{endpointUrl}}?page=-1

### Test 11: Invalid page (non-numeric)
### Expected: 400 Bad Request - page must be a number
GET {{endpointUrl}}?page=abc

### Test 12: Invalid limit (zero)
### Expected: 400 Bad Request - limit must be at least 1
GET {{endpointUrl}}?limit=0

### Test 13: Invalid limit (exceeds maximum)
### Expected: 400 Bad Request - limit must be at most 100
GET {{endpointUrl}}?limit=101

### Test 14: Invalid limit (non-numeric)
### Expected: 400 Bad Request - limit must be a number
GET {{endpointUrl}}?limit=fifty

### ============================================================================
### EDGE CASES
### ============================================================================

### Test 15: Case sensitivity test (uppercase search)
### Expected: 200 OK with case-insensitive match
GET {{endpointUrl}}?search=UJI
